[SN]TITLE[SN]
Charlie Colkett, Islam Feruz and Fankaty Dabo: Chelsea trio join Swindon on loan

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Swindon have signed defender Fankaty Dabo, midfielder Charlie Colkett and striker Islam Feruz on loan from Premier League leaders Chelsea.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
England Under-20 international Dabo, 21, is yet to make his professional debut.
Feruz, 21 has had loan spells with Blackpool and Hibernian while Colkett, 20, was recently recalled from a loan at Bristol Rovers.
The trio could feature against Bolton in League One on Saturday.
